    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=s78isrsy9x]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=s78isrsy9x]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=rdfeswv6uk]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=rdfeswv6uk]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ezl6p9okac]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ezl6p9okac]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=caefx733zk]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=caefx733zk]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296015392&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=759\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608829457/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296015392&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1073\" data-width=\"1074\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608829480\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608829457\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"872ec470-3f5f-479c-88ca-51de68beb389\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296015392&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1074&amp;height=1073 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296015392&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=759 1x\" /></span><h2 id=\"BestPractices-WoodTable-WoodTable\">Wood Table</h2><p>The table utilizes several different texture maps. </p><p /><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"rdfeswv6uk\">Diffuse Map</span></strong></p><p>One is for the diffuse (sometimes called albedo) color, which controls the actual color variation and result for the wood. This is the most basic form of color mapping for objects and is independent of reflection color and other material effects.</p><p /><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"caefx733zk\">Specular Map</span></strong></p><p>Another is a specular map used to define the amount and locations of reflection and highlights on the surface. </p><p>This map can define the color of a reflection as well as its strength across the surface. Some variation here is essential for realism unless you're creating a product render where the object is new and perfectly untouched. Scratches and other defects can be added. </p><p>Take care to match these effects with other useful maps, like a bump map, so that the surface features are all accounted for correctly. You probably wouldn't want a surface with scratches and wear without a matching bump map. You may notice this is dark; you'll find that the PxrSurface specular color is sensitive to light values and can become bright quickly.</p><p /><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ezl6p9okac\">Roughness Map</span></strong></p><p>A roughness map adds variation in the specular map roughness result. </p><p>Few objects in the real world have perfectly mirror-like surfaces, and objects with a rougher, glossy finish are rarely uniform in their appearance. Controlling this with a texture map will help provide realism and create signs of wear and use across the table. It's useful for things like fingerprints, smudges, grease marks, wear from rubbing and touching, or natural variation in the manufactured materials.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"DiffuseTable.jpg\" width=\"221\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/DiffuseTable.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758296396261&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=221&amp;height=221\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608829457/DiffuseTable.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758296396261&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607846839\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DiffuseTable.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608829457\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"02dd2619-6609-48b2-930a-23bb58199016\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/DiffuseTable.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758296396261&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=442 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/DiffuseTable.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758296396261&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=221&amp;height=221 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"SpecularTable.jpg\" width=\"221\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/SpecularTable.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296399736&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=221&amp;height=221\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608829457/SpecularTable.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296399736&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608665708\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"SpecularTable.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608829457\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"f44634b8-4765-4d93-bddf-6c4c3a4ccdc3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/SpecularTable.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296399736&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=442 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/SpecularTable.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296399736&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=221&amp;height=221 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"GlossinessTable.jpg\" width=\"221\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/GlossinessTable.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296402875&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=221&amp;height=221\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608829457/GlossinessTable.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296402875&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608141884\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"GlossinessTable.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608829457\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"de386265-dc1c-4b24-bfb4-df9b52b17698\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/GlossinessTable.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296402875&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=442 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/GlossinessTable.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296402875&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=221&amp;height=221 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"cbc0f1ae-d59d-4e61-92c5-ae8896c372bf\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Of course, there are many other types of maps that are used in CGI.  Metalness, anisotropic, subsurface, and emission maps are typical, but we&rsquo;re not going to worry about those in this best practice example.</p><p>RenderMan has a unique bump map system called <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542222907\" rel=\"nofollow\">BumpRoughness</a>.</p></div></div><p /><p /><hr /><h3 id=\"BestPractices-WoodTable-NextSteps\"><span data-colorid=\"s78isrsy9x\">Next Steps</span></h3><p>Nice .. that&rsquo;s the table explained and the types of maps used to create the shader.  In the next lesson, we&rsquo;ll take a look at the metal tray.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/608862209/Best+Practices+-+Textures\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608862209\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"previousLesson.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/previousLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296015039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608829457/previousLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296015039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"67\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608829477\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"previousLesson.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608829457\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"9843fa9e-c226-4b1b-9693-c4475d95042b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/previousLesson.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758296015039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=67 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608829457/previousLesson.png?v